<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT4">
<l>āṟu caṭaikkarantā ṉaṇṭarkōṉ ṟaṉṉōṭuṅ</l>
<l>kūṟuṭaiya ṉeṉpatuvuṅ koḷkaittē vēṟoruva</l>
<l>rillāmai niṉṟāṉai yemmāṉai yepporuṭkuñ</l>
<l>collāṉaic coṉṉēṉ tokuttu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it acceptable to say that [Śiva] who concealed the river in [his] matted locks,</l>
<l>Shares [supremacy] with the King of the celestials?</l>
<l>I have summed Him up, who is the word for all meanings, our Lord,</l>
<l>Him who has stood without another [to match Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
